casebody.data:
Jason Eugene BUSH, petitioner,
v.
ARIZONA. No. 18-7235. Supreme Court of the United States April 15, 2019.

Motion of respondent for leave to file brief in opposition with the appendix under seal granted. Motion of petitioner for *1547leave to file reply brief under seal with redacted copies for the public record granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Arizona denied.
